  "title": "SearchBox#onReset test no longer passes",
  "body": "see https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch.js/pull/4156#discussion_r331552971\r\n\r\nIt seems like the `reset` event no longer is triggered after migrating to preact X, the tests have been updated, but the event doesn't get called correctly\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/algolia/instantsearch.js/blob/92a21308a272e391de726a47bfaf84e794077697/src/components/SearchBox/__tests__/SearchBox-test.js#L288-L345\r\n\r\nWe suspected JSDOM initially, but it seems the event does get fired. This means it's enzyme which doesn't trigger the event correctly.",
